---
title: Cherry Ancho Chicken with Roasted Carrots & Scallion Rice
description: Our chefs are always brainstorming ways to make “chicken for dinner” a little more awesome. The delicious twist this week: a dynamic pan sauce with cherry jam, ancho chili powder, rich demi-glace, and a squeeze of lemon juice. Sweet and savory is the name of the game here, with the sides being no exception. Roasted carrots tossed with lemon zest and scallion-studded rice pair perfectly with the smoky-sweet chicken. Get ready for a flavor explosion.
